sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant BFF as BFF Layer
    participant IdeaServices as Idea Services
    participant DB as Postgres Database [Read Store]

    %% Idea Search/Filter Flow By Evaluator
    User->>UI: 1. Invoke Search/List/Filter Idea by Evaluator
    
    UI->>APIGateway: 2. Send Search Request<br/>(Search Criteria)
    Note over UI,APIGateway: GET/POST /api/ideas/search<br/>Parameters: filters, pagination
    
    APIGateway->>BFF: 3. Forward Request to BFF
    Note over APIGateway,BFF: Request Validation<br/>& Authentication Check
    
    BFF->>IdeaServices: 4. Route to Idea Query Service
    
    %% Database Query Operations
    alt Search by Idea
        IdeaServices->>DB: 5a. Query by Idea Name/ID
        DB-->>IdeaServices: 6a. Return Idea Results
    else Search by User
        IdeaService->>DB: 5b. Query by User/Owner
        DB-->>IdeaServices: 6b. Return  Ideas by USer
    else Search by Date
        IdeaService->>DB: 5c. Query by Date Range
        DB-->>IdeaServices: 6c. Return Date-Filtered Ideas
    else List All (with Filters)
        IdeaService->>DB: 5d. Query with Multiple Filters
        DB-->>IdeaServices: 6d. Return Filtered Results
    end
    
    %% Response Processing
    IdeaServices-->>BFF: 7. Return Idea Data (JSON)
    
    BFF-->>APIGateway: 8. Aggregate & Transform Response
    
    APIGateway-->>UI: 9. Return JSON Response
    Note over APIGateway,UI: HTTP 200 OK<br/>Content-Type: application/json
    
    UI-->>User: 10. Display Idea Results
    Note over UI,User: Render campaign list<br/>with search/filter options
    
    %% Error Handling
    alt Error Scenario
        IdeaServices->>DB: Query Execution
        DB-->>IdeaServices: Error Response
        IdeaService-->>BFF: Error Details
        BFF-->>APIGateway: Formatted Error
        APIGateway-->>UI: HTTP Error (400/500)
        UI-->>User: Display Error Message
    end